          "reviewBody": "Basant valley public school is in sector 46 Gurgaon. This is a public school till class 5th. Location is very good in a jalvihar colony. I recommend this school for the startup. Teachers are well trained and well behaved, treat the childrens in such a great way. Transport facility is available here. The fees is quite high. Only one minus point is that they focus on holiday much more. In Saturday school also closed but many other schools are open. Teaching is good in this school. You can choose this school for your kids. Special activities are also organised by the management.\nGood school in my view.",
